trans-unit.source: The ReplicationCursor class represents a replication operation occurrence.
trans-unit.target: 复制游标类表示发生复制操作。

trans-unit.source: Gets the time of the last successful replication synchronization with the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: 获取与复制源服务器的上次成功复制同步的时间。

trans-unit.source: The LastSuccessfulSyncTime indicates the time when this domain controller last synchronized to changes for this partition on the source directory system agent (DSA).
trans-unit.target: LastSuccessfulSyncTime 指示当此域控制器上一次同步到此分区源目录系统代理 (DSA) 上的更改的时间。

trans-unit.source: The time at which the last successful replication synchronization occurred.
trans-unit.target: 上次成功复制同步发生的时间。

trans-unit.source: This property is not supported on [!INCLUDE[Win2kFamily](~/add/includes/win2kfamily-md.md)].
Gets the name of the partition to which this replication operation was applied.
trans-unit.target: 获取此复制操作已应用到的分区的名称。

trans-unit.source: The name of the partition represented by this replication cursor.
trans-unit.target: 表示由该复制游标的分区名称。

trans-unit.source: Gets the invocation identifier of the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: 获取复制源服务器的调用标识符。

trans-unit.source: The invocation identifier of the replication source server
trans-unit.target: 复制源服务器调用标识符

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the replication source server.
trans-unit.target: 获取复制源服务器的名称。

trans-unit.source: The name of the replication source server.
Gets the maximum update sequence number (USN) for which the destination server has accepted changes from the source server.
trans-unit.target: 获取为其目标服务器已接受来自源服务器的更改的最大更新序列号 (USN)。

trans-unit.source: The maximum update sequence number (USN) for which the destination server has accepted changes from the source server.
trans-unit.target: 最大更新序列号 (USN) 目标服务器已为其接受来自源服务器的更改。
